headline: Karen and Kevin Lynch Commit $5 Million to Advance Leadership and Student Success
summary: BOCA RATON, Fla., August 25, 2025--Lynn University today announced a transformative $5 million gift from Karen and Kevin Lynch to establish the Karen S. Lynch Center for Leadership and Social Impact and create endowed support for new leadership programs and student scholarships.
